data.description: Welcome to this RARE, TRUE 4 BEDROOM HOME IN THE HEART OF BLACKLICK! Move right in! It is freshly painted throughout, updated LVT flooring, new lights and fixtures, kitchen hood. The dramatic, 2-story Great Room flows into Dining Room and into the enormous, eat-in kitchen with an island and tons of cabinet and counter space PLUS a pantry and fenced backyard. The second floor boasts FOUR, large bedrooms all with ceiling fans, including the master suite with vaulted ceilings, large walk-in closet, and private bath with a double vanity! You have lots of storage in the TWO, easy-access crawl spaces in the basement! The home is on a quiet street, steps from the neighborhood park! Minutes from shopping, dining and freeways! Additional updates; Roof 2018, AC, Hot water tank, refrigerator-2021.
